# CodeAlpha Machine Learning Internship Projects

This repository contains all projects completed during my **CodeAlpha Machine Learning Internship**. Each project focuses on solving real-world problems using Machine Learning, Data Analysis, and interactive web applications built with Python.

The objective of this repository is to demonstrate practical implementation of the complete Machine Learning workflow, including data preprocessing, feature engineering, model training, evaluation, prediction, and deployment through professional Streamlit dashboards.

---

## Repository Structure

```
CodeAlpha_Tasks/
│
├── CodeAlpha_CreditLens/
│   ├── Credit risk prediction project
│   └── Streamlit dashboard
│
├── CodeAlpha_HealthSense/
│   ├── Multi-disease prediction system
│   └── Streamlit dashboard
│
└── README.md
```

---

## Projects

### 1. CreditLens

An end-to-end Machine Learning application for predicting customer loan default risk.

**Highlights**

- Automated data preprocessing
- Feature engineering pipeline
- Multiple ML algorithms
- Best model selection
- Probability-based predictions
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- Production-ready workflow

---

### 2. HealthSense AI

A Machine Learning based healthcare application capable of predicting multiple diseases from patient information.

**Highlights**

- Multi-disease prediction
- Automatic dataset detection
- Automated preprocessing
- Separate model for each disease
- Patient-friendly prediction workflow
- Doctor review system
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard

---

