## Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/jitenhudda/CodeAlpha_Tasks.git
```

Move into the repository

```bash
cd CodeAlpha_Tasks
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Running Individual Projects

Navigate to any project folder and follow its instructions to train models and launch the Streamlit application.

Example:

```bash
cd CodeAlpha_HealthSense
streamlit run app.py
```

or

```bash
cd CodeAlpha_CreditLens
streamlit run app.py
```

